"[{\"handle\":\"@lxfater\",\"name\":\"铁锤人\",\"text\":\"我只是说了Hermes的原创性上不如OpenClaw\\n\\n突然就出现一批老外来反驳我了\\n\\n我做自媒体的人角度观察：OpenClaw当时的热度是100的话，这个的热度是5吧。\\n\\n起码现在是，所以他不会比OpenClaw出名。\\n\\n因为要融资了吗？管理得这么严格。\\n\\n有名有比不上OpenClaw，好用又打不过Claude\",\"likes\":31,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":21,\"views\":13926,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T03:43:16.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/lxfater/status/2043535466495119854\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@phibrowser\",\"name\":\"Phi Browser\",\"text\":\"Phi Browser is here: a polished native macOS browser with an AI that has soul, fully observable browser memory that grows with you, scheduled background tasks that keep things moving, and equipped with cli/mcp to work with your agents. Built on Chromium, open-source as well.\",\"likes\":1106,\"retweets\":111,\"replies\":0,\"views\":9553869,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/phibrowser/status/2039906759423463854/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@geekbb\",\"name\":\"Geek\",\"text\":\"我已经不关心 OpenClaw 更新了，我的任务在 Hermes 上基本是一轮游，一次搞定。使用 GPT-5.4 比在 OpenClaw 省多了，两个 Plus 帐号现在也够用，以后不够我就再花十几元去买来补充。这是一个美好的时期~\",\"likes\":318,\"retweets\":6,\"replies\":53,\"views\":72907,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T03:09:40.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/geekbb/status/2043164620949758013\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@EvaCmore\",\"name\":\"Eva 树姐\",\"text\":\"恭喜还没学习怎么用OpenClaw的人，可以不用学习了。\\n\\n直接学习怎么安装Hermes，怎么用Hermes。\\n\\n最近大家对AI的焦虑感应该降低很多了，因为很难一直追上，适合自己的才是最好的，比如我现在最喜欢用的还是GPT。\",\"likes\":80,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":28,\"views\":14082,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:48:12.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/EvaCmore/status/2043325315125284967\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@KKaWSB\",\"name\":\"KK.aWSB\",\"text\":\"Nous Research开源了hermes-agent-self-evolution——一个让AI agent自己进化自己prompt的代码库，\\n\\n背后引擎叫GEPA，ICLR 2026 Oral，比强化学习少用35倍数据，效果还高出20个百分点。\\n\\n别再手调system prompt了。prompt工程这件事，正在被prompt自己取代。\",\"likes\":1401,\"retweets\":182,\"replies\":18,\"views\":69344,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T00:08:47.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/KKaWSB/status/2043119101028274268\",\"external_links\":[\"GitHub - NousResearch/hermes-agent-self-evolution:  Evolutionary self-improvement for Hermes Agent...\",\"来自 github.com\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@MrLarus\",\"name\":\"Larus Canus\",\"text\":\"OpenClaw和Hermes浅用对比：\\n\\n1、直观感受：OpenClaw比较慢比较耗token，Hermes比较快比较省，大概30%。\\n\\n2、回复模式：OpenClaw之所以慢，有一部分原因是没有披露执行明细，而Hermes会，也就是\\n@yetone\\n 说的把 trajectory\",\"likes\":348,\"retweets\":48,\"replies\":19,\"views\":47698,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T06:33:11.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/MrLarus/status/2043215836521902444\",\"external_links\":[\"GitHub - joeynyc/hermes-hudui: Web UI consciousness monitor for Hermes — the AI agent with persis...\",\"来自 github.com\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@dingyi\",\"name\":\"Ding\",\"text\":\"又发现一个很像 cmux 的。\\n\\n\\nhttps://\\nonorca.dev\",\"likes\":63,\"retweets\":9,\"replies\":13,\"views\":13740,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T10:56:59.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dingyi/status/2043282225354129894\",\"external_links\":[\"https://onorca.dev\"],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@Samaytwt\",\"name\":\"Samay\",\"text\":\"Be honest As developers, you have $20.\\n\\nWhat are you buying ?\\n\\n> Claude\\n> Codex\",\"likes\":163,\"retweets\":5,\"replies\":96,\"views\":4229,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:49:49.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Samaytwt/status/2043552213138825253\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@wangdefou\",\"name\":\"得否\",\"text\":\"晚上安装了一下 hermes agent \\n配置起来还是挺简单的\\n\\nOpenClaw也好，hermes agent也好\\n都只是工具\\n最终还是要基于需求来使用\\n\\n还是要回归需求\\n纯折腾工具也没啥意思\",\"likes\":28,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":16,\"views\":3396,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T15:51:43.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/wangdefou/status/2043356397807812619\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Khazix0918\",\"name\":\"数字生命卡兹克\",\"text\":\"人生感觉最舒适的状态，就是可以不为生计而发愁。永远无时无刻的自由的创造。\\n现在拉屎的时候都在拿着手机跟Claude Code进行Coding创造。\\n好爽。\",\"likes\":51,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":14,\"views\":4118,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:59:11.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Khazix0918/status/2043554569779892628\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@StandDOTtrade\",\"name\":\"Stand\",\"text\":\"0% copy trading fees. Where do you Stand?\",\"likes\":944,\"retweets\":287,\"replies\":0,\"views\":3115951,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/StandDOTtrade/status/2042332911404298466/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@supezen\",\"name\":\"ZEN\",\"text\":\"试用一下 Ghostty \\n据说启动速度非常快，内存占用更低；由于 GPU 加速渲染，滚动和显示更流畅。\",\"likes\":11,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":3,\"views\":5355,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:06:19.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/supezen/status/2043586562378858921\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@0xVeryBigOrange\",\"name\":\"很大很大的橙子\",\"text\":\"我受不了中国大模型了，回新加坡换龙虾模型，中国厂商做的模型狗都不用，回去换codex。\\n\\n他妈的就是个弱智，昨天把我调试的血压都要升高了，个傻逼模型。\",\"likes\":51,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":29,\"views\":20518,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T02:00:09.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/0xVeryBigOrange/status/2043509514528588204\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@ShenHuang_\",\"name\":\"Shen Huang\",\"text\":\"说句得罪人的：\\n\\n觉得 Opus 降智的人，大部分是把 Agent 框架的问题归咎到模型上了。\\n\\nClaude Code 最近在疯狂优化 token 效率 — 压缩上下文、缩短 thinking、路由轻量模式。\\n\\n本质上 Anthropic 在把 Claude Code 往动态算力分配的方向做：简单问题少转几圈，难题多转几圈。\\n\\n这对 Anthropic\",\"likes\":58,\"retweets\":9,\"replies\":30,\"views\":27589,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T18:36:19.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ShenHuang_/status/2043397819806175371\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@corvuschen1211\",\"name\":\"陈尔冬是你大爷\",\"text\":\"给Hermes投喂了一份记忆文档，被Hermes振聋发聩的提问惊呆了...\",\"likes\":179,\"retweets\":11,\"replies\":16,\"views\":70286,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T09:39:07.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/corvuschen1211/status/2043262629347827759\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@brucexu_eth\",\"name\":\"brucexu.eth\",\"text\":\"不知道为什么，Openclaw 总给我有一点怪怪的感觉。感觉不够安全而且很冗余庞大。\\n\\n然后 Hermes Agent 就爽很多。然后已经配置好了，而且逐步在优化和增强，目前感觉还是挺好的。看着越来越多的人倒戈，感觉 OpenClaw 正在面临很大的挑战。\",\"likes\":56,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":12,\"views\":9571,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T10:05:14.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/brucexu_eth/status/2043269202375848220\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@himself65\",\"name\":\"Bread\",\"text\":\"Opus一天比一天傻，当初GPT5也是，\\n这个行业模式到最后没有人敢订阅年费会员\",\"likes\":596,\"retweets\":15,\"replies\":80,\"views\":95723,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T02:57:21.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/himself65/status/2043161520696447107\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dontbesilent\",\"name\":\"dontbesilent\",\"text\":\"Twitter 上有一些应该是完全看不懂中文的人在关注我\\n\\n是不是他们刷到我的时候就不是中文？\\n\\n他们那边开始自动翻译了？\",\"likes\":31,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":20,\"views\":12571,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T17:58:28.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dontbesilent/status/2043388296487944368\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@appwrite\",\"name\":\"Appwrite\",\"text\":\"Opus 4.6 lately\",\"likes\":4395,\"retweets\":384,\"replies\":61,\"views\":349388,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T11:50:45.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/appwrite/status/2043295754790535538\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Crypto_Cat888\",\"name\":\"CryptoCat|猫姐\",\"text\":\"来自靠谱程序员朋友的测评：\\n\\n真的建议你们体验一下Hermes ，比较之下，龙虾就是垃圾\\n\\nAI时代学的慢的，可能真就不用学了\",\"likes\":101,\"retweets\":11,\"replies\":19,\"views\":49031,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T16:26:05.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Crypto_Cat888/status/2043365044566802677\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@DITOGAMESch\",\"name\":\"DITOGAMES\",\"text\":\"If you have a mouse, you have to play this game.\",\"likes\":0,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":0,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/DITOGAMESch/status/2040018467667988588/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Adidotdev\",\"name\":\"Adit_Yah\",\"text\":\"Devs be honest, which IDE is the best right now?\",\"likes\":511,\"retweets\":31,\"replies\":193,\"views\":157869,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T15:47:28.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Adidotdev/status/2043355328889356352\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dotey\",\"name\":\"宝玉\",\"text\":\"Cursor Agent 3.0 被曝“套壳” Claude Code，官方回应称为小范围测试\\n\\nCursor 的新版 Agent 被曝出“套壳”了 Anthropic 的底层技术。开发者逆向分析发现，Cursor 3.0 版本在本地运行了一个替换引擎，简单粗暴地把系统提示词和消息里的“Claude”字眼全部替换成了“Cursor”。其安装包里直接内置了 Anthropic\",\"likes\":58,\"retweets\":17,\"replies\":17,\"views\":28878,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:14:57.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dotey/status/2043588734952563180\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@linwanwan823\",\"name\":\"林晚晚的猫\",\"text\":\"被AMD的人实锤了，Claude最近这股「降智」味儿，是Anthropic亲手调出来的。\\n\\nAMD的AI总监扒了Anthropic的数据，\\nClaude的思考中位数从2200掉到了600，\\n每次编辑前的阅读次数从6.6x掉到2x。\\n\\n晚晚我查了一下，\\n这就好比本来要琢磨10分钟才动手的人， \\n现在3分钟就开始乱写。 \\n直接腰斩了两次。\",\"likes\":72,\"retweets\":7,\"replies\":17,\"views\":9522,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:59:50.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/linwanwan823/status/2043600031505375610\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Yonah_x\",\"name\":\"汉松\",\"text\":\"试用了一周的 Hermes，我觉得已经能够完全替代 OpenClaw 了。\\n\\nHermes 升级从来没有挂过，再也不用在升级的时候提心吊胆。\\n\\n再见，龙虾。\",\"likes\":90,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":11,\"views\":20863,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T11:17:21.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Yonah_x/status/2043287350722412570\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@lidangzzz\",\"name\":\"lidang 立党 （全网劝人卖房、劝人学CS、劝人买SP500和NASDAQ100第一人）\",\"text\":\"总有人说，“有了AI就能做所有的软件，SaaS必然会死掉，可以彻底替代程序员”，结果一看产出的内容，全是小表单、小前端、贪吃蛇、小App、小助手，\\n\\n我问，Zoom挣这么多钱，你怎么不做一个Zoom出来？你知道Zoom的架构吗？Zoom如何做到encoder和decoder在不同架构、不同CPU/GPU、不同设备上适配？\",\"likes\":623,\"retweets\":72,\"replies\":58,\"views\":102355,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T04:08:39.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/lidangzzz/status/2043179464700420451\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@xiaojietongxue\",\"name\":\"肖师傅\",\"text\":\"刚才一个新客户找我谈AI项目，我跟他说，你在福建能找到一个做到我这水平的人，你的费用我出一半，但如果你找不到，你再找我，我的价格要涨30%，你敢不敢赌一下！对方有点被我的气势吓到了，估计很快可以成交！\",\"likes\":9,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":11,\"views\":891,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T08:54:58.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/xiaojietongxue/status/2043613905566540167\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@billtheinvestor\",\"name\":\"Bill The Investor\",\"text\":\"在 GitHub上搜索 OPENAI_API_KEY，一堆API 密钥\\n\\n傻子们都在标榜自己是vibe coder，真好\",\"likes\":860,\"retweets\":105,\"replies\":55,\"views\":247560,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T19:05:55.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/billtheinvestor/status/2043405270781772244\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@LuBtc888\",\"name\":\"0x鸣人\",\"text\":\"世界上最通人性的两个平台：\\n\\n𝕏      闲鱼\\n\\n别问我为什么！！\",\"likes\":10,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":20,\"views\":17927,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:41:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/LuBtc888/status/2043565092101644563\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@vista8\",\"name\":\"向阳乔木\",\"text\":\"还是对deepseek这家公司心存敬意，心无旁骛追求AGI。\\n\\n配合适配国产显卡虽然耽误了进度，但长期看对整个AI行业打破垄断要好。\\n\\n据说已经随时可以发布v4，出手必定是开源sota，即使不再如v3版本震撼。\\n\\n降低预期就好，希望国内多一些这类公司，另外身边朋友都看好智谱\",\"likes\":172,\"retweets\":8,\"replies\":49,\"views\":31441,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:10:19.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/vista8/status/2043542270243414499\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@ChartThrea42555\",\"name\":\"ChartThread\",\"text\":\"Most breakouts fail.\\nStop guessing.\\nSee how price reacts to levels.\",\"likes\":28,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":0,\"views\":207717,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ChartThrea42555/status/2041849325634863568/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@kevinma_dev_zh\",\"name\":\"Kevin Ma\",\"text\":\"今天大多时间都在用 claude code 的 remote control 处理工作，不得不说确实太香了\",\"likes\":15,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":8,\"views\":6012,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:49:29.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/kevinma_dev_zh/status/2043325636882956574\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@vasuman\",\"name\":\"vas\",\"text\":\"Claude Code is unusable and Codex is incredible\",\"likes\":262,\"retweets\":9,\"replies\":79,\"views\":15232,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:54:29.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/vasuman/status/2043568486757310758\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Pluvio9yte\",\"name\":\"雪踏乌云\",\"text\":\"建议每一个Vibe Coding用户都配置一个终端管理应用。\\n\\n比如我之前用了几天的iterm2，现在切换到了图中的ghostty。\\n\\n为什么使用CLI管理：\\n\\n1.我们习惯使用 CLI 进行 Vibe Coding 的用户，在执行、调试、跑项目、管多 session、快速切换上下文等很多场景，基本都是在终端。\\n\\n2.流畅、GPU\",\"likes\":37,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":19,\"views\":14127,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T02:28:43.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Pluvio9yte/status/2043516705574736226\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@geekbb\",\"name\":\"Geek\",\"text\":\"我发现 Hermes 在终端下使用，对 Dark 模式很友好，换成 Light 就白瞎了，换了几个主题，打的字都是看不到。\",\"likes\":31,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":13,\"views\":8193,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T03:01:01.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/geekbb/status/2043524831925486023\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@sharesight\",\"name\":\"Sharesight - investment portfolio tracker\",\"text\":\"Investors: want to see the true performance of your stocks, ETFs, dividends & more that your broker doesn't show? \\n\\nTry Sharesight for FREE today & easily keep track of all of your investments in one place\",\"likes\":284,\"retweets\":44,\"replies\":0,\"views\":1165194,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/sharesight/status/2023931780412436893/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@jakevin7\",\"name\":\"卡比卡比\",\"text\":\"录了一期博客，和 AB 聊了一下 AI agent 时代的一些我的看法，和整个自己创造的演进思路。\\n\\n链接在评论\",\"likes\":31,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":3,\"views\":2863,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:05:03.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/jakevin7/status/2043556044908183702\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@manateelazycat\",\"name\":\"Andy Stewart\",\"text\":\"我分别问了 OpenClaw 和 Hermes： 你们怎么看AI Agent的未来？ \\n\\n他们俩果然性格不一样啊，想法也不一样，有意思\",\"likes\":2,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":2,\"views\":2747,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T14:25:43.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/manateelazycat/status/2043334756058927529\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@ThisisHan1_\",\"name\":\"Han1\",\"text\":\"沉寂了很久，今天终于可以发布最近做的东西——\\n\\nAntenna \\n让你手中的OpenClaw/Hermes/Claude Code基于对你的了解帮你找到身边适合你的人\",\"likes\":58,\"retweets\":6,\"replies\":9,\"views\":8546,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T23:30:07.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ThisisHan1_/status/2043471758393836031\",\"external_links\":[\"Antenna — AI-Powered Social Discovery\",\"来自 antenna.fyi\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@CTracy0803\",\"name\":\"Tracy\",\"text\":\"在所有用户群体里最怕程序员，他们完全没有忠诚度可言，哪个好用哪个便宜就用哪个。\\n\\n而且他们善于学习，对价格和质量非常敏锐，几乎不存在信息差。\\n\\n做他们的生意太难了\",\"likes\":7,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":9,\"views\":751,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T08:08:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/CTracy0803/status/2043602085854187758\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@hylarucoder\",\"name\":\"海拉鲁编程客\",\"text\":\"最近实践了一些 harness engineering ，我在 AGENTS/CLAUDE.md 加了一个原则章节用于指挥 coding agent\\n\\n个人觉得蛮好用的， 推荐给大家试试。\\n\\n## 原则\\n\\n1. 代码仓库是唯一的记录系统：不在 repo 里的知识对智能体不存在。讨论、脑中决策、外部文档——如果影响开发，必须落地为 repo 内的 versioned\",\"likes\":369,\"retweets\":68,\"replies\":16,\"views\":22128,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T05:39:36.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/hylarucoder/status/2043202352447189368\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@howie_serious\",\"name\":\"howie.serious\",\"text\":\"思考题：大家都发现了 claude opus 疯狂降智，那么，背后的结构性原因是什么？暗示我们应该关注哪些股票？\",\"likes\":15,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":12,\"views\":6760,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T08:19:18.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/howie_serious/status/2043604931526181099\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@imwsl90\",\"name\":\"卫斯理\",\"text\":\"雷子投了Hermes Agent?\",\"likes\":15,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":5,\"views\":10045,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T00:47:27.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/imwsl90/status/2043491217535885477\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dontbesilent\",\"name\":\"dontbesilent\",\"text\":\"有个朋友在国内卖智能体小程序，买家非常下沉\\n\\n他也觉得这个事不太好，想转型卖真正能解决问题的东西\\n\\n现在面临最大的阻碍是：运行新产品，买家起码要有个电脑，很多人没有电脑不知道怎么说服他们购买\\n\\n（现在知道为啥鸿蒙平板当 PC 卖能卖掉了吧\",\"likes\":67,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":9,\"views\":10635,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:23:06.000Z\",\"