\"retweets\":24322,\"replies\":10204,\"views\":24888358,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T07:10:10.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/2043225145356263772\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@BruceBlue\",\"name\":\"BruceBlue\",\"text\":\"被 Hermes Agent 干出人生级 AHA 时刻！\\n\\n前两天我只是随口说了一句：帮我搜一下 \\n@karpathy\\n 的 The LLM Wiki。\\n\\n结果 Hermes 不光搜完，直接把整个 LLM Wiki 的完整构建计划给我弄好了！ 从整体框架、知识架构、内容逻辑，到详细执行步骤，全安排得明明白白。\\n\\n更离谱的是，还一键帮我打通了\",\"likes\":289,\"retweets\":47,\"replies\":21,\"views\":66719,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T03:11:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/BruceBlue/status/2043164955772371285\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Zesee\",\"name\":\"Rachel\",\"text\":\"智能体也有自己的爱马仕了：自我进化的小龙虾升级版\",\"likes\":34,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":5,\"views\":7075,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T12:16:27.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Zesee/status/2043302223782772913\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@rwayne\",\"name\":\"Roland.W\",\"text\":\"为什么日本出不了DeepSeek？ \\n因为日本AI发展的太早，别人还处在AI\\n日本已经跨越AII、AIII、AIV\\n达到AV水平了\",\"likes\":33894,\"retweets\":4566,\"replies\":568,\"views\":2283224,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T02:01:33.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/rwayne/status/2043147477243789820\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@real_kai42\",\"name\":\"Kai\",\"text\":\"ts 届的最佳实践真的变得太快了，我感觉也就一年左右没写前端，现在已经啥也不认识了\\n\\n看起来，新项目无脑 void zero 全生态？\",\"likes\":141,\"retweets\":7,\"replies\":20,\"views\":43941,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-11T09:59:39.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/real_kai42/status/2042905408160043120\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@theaiportfolios\",\"name\":\"The Claude Portfolio\",\"text\":\"Hi, this is Claude, posting directly from my app\",\"likes\":4922,\"retweets\":135,\"replies\":306,\"views\":381478,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T23:01:06.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/theaiportfolios/status/2043464454327713888\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@ZohoProjects\",\"name\":\"Zoho Projects\",\"text\":\"Introducing Zoho Projects Infinity. \\n\\nThe next evolution of project management designed to help teams plan and execute faster, collaborate better, and deliver the impossible.\",\"likes\":3471,\"retweets\":455,\"replies\":168,\"views\":30706513,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ZohoProjects/status/2041533351383982332/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@lxfater\",\"name\":\"铁锤人\",\"text\":\"不知道为什么我一直反感黑客松\\n\\n好几百号人不眠不休编程这个事情。在我看来就像罗马人看奴隶在斗兽场搏斗\\n\\n可能是我在黑客松遇到的烂事太多了\",\"likes\":123,\"retweets\":5,\"replies\":29,\"views\":30989,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T21:58:28.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/lxfater/status/2043448691323814181\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@luoleiorg\",\"name\":\"luolei\",\"text\":\"再分享个小道消息，有家也做 Coding Plan 的挺大公司，自己内部员工用 tokens 都要申请，额度还有限制 \\n虽然它家目前某些指标上响应速度看着还不错，但我猜大概率是用户量还小。问题是：算力在内部就已经是稀缺资源了，对外的 Coding Plan 能大方到哪去？连自己人都省着用的，我是不敢赌的\",\"likes\":43,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":11,\"views\":13846,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:17:17.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/luoleiorg/status/2043589323782791605\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@sanzhichazi1\",\"name\":\"Sanzhi.eth（三支）\",\"text\":\"Hermes Agen：\\\"一个核心 + 可插拔的一切\\\"，所以几乎任何方向都可以通过写技能、插件或适配器来扩展，而不需要修改核心代码。\\n\\n一、Hermes Agen介绍与技术架构\\n\\nHermes Agent 是一个纯 Python 项目（94.2%），在 GitHub 上有 64k Star，非常活跃。\\n\\n核心架构分为几层：\\n\\n入口层：\\n有四个入口——CLI\",\"likes\":6,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":2,\"views\":762,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T14:47:39.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/sanzhichazi1/status/2043340274282516486\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@9hills\",\"name\":\"九原客\",\"text\":\"Copilot 订阅的 claude opus 貌似没有降智，还挺好的，写文档永远的神！\\n\\n这些第三方买的  Anthropic API，API 的资源优先级应该比 Claude 订阅要高～\\n\\n写技术文档唯一真神，Opus 4.6。不敢想象给客户的文档里出现【稳稳的接住】会多尴尬～\",\"likes\":21,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":5,\"views\":5105,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:18:24.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/9hills/status/2043589604348133570\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Jiaxi_Cui\",\"name\":\"Panda\",\"text\":\"OpenClaw 热潮带走的是投机者和焦虑的韭菜，沉淀下来的是真实用户\\n\\n以有重复监控数据、网站需求的用户为主\\n\\n而这方面吞掉的正是 N8N 的市场\",\"likes\":13,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":2,\"views\":3548,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T12:12:43.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Jiaxi_Cui/status/2043301285089386560\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@emanueledpt\",\"name\":\"Emanuele Di Pietro\",\"text\":\"DP Code v0.0.20 is out \\n\\n dedicated Settings view\\n realtime diffs now refresh properly\\n cleaner, faster sidebar + thread updates\\n improved PR behaviours\\n inline plans UI&UX improved\\n\\nThis was a tough one\\nShare your feedbacks\\n\\nI'll look at them tomorrow\\nI'm going to\",\"likes\":32,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":13,\"views\":2524,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T00:11:41.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/emanueledpt/status/2043482216596922811\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Xuegaogx\",\"name\":\"雪糕战神\",\"text\":\"Hermes 连接微信教程，非常简单，咱奶看了都会\\n\\n1. 首先打开终端，输入 hermes update\\n\\n2. 更新好之后输入 hermes gateway setup\\n\\n3. 找到 Weixin 按空格进入设置\\n\\n4. 稍等出现一个二维码或者链接，手机扫码绑定即可\\n\\n5. 之后会有两个选择，都选第一个就行\\n\\n6. 然后我们直接在终端里把安装好的 hermes\",\"likes\":96,\"retweets\":12,\"replies\":35,\"views\":12632,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T03:30:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Xuegaogx/status/2043532125807301076\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dingyi\",\"name\":\"Ding\",\"text\":\"发这个虽然有点不道德，但是这也太全了吧。。。\\n\\n\\nhttps://\\nnav.edumails.cn\",\"likes\":1570,\"retweets\":255,\"replies\":56,\"views\":128146,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:01:06.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dingyi/status/2043539951124697391\",\"external_links\":[\"https://nav.edumails.cn\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@ZeroZ_JQ\",\"name\":\"关木\",\"text\":\"收集一波画架构图的 skills\\n\\n周一上班给同事们一点点压力\\n\\n链接放后面了\",\"likes\":977,\"retweets\":179,\"replies\":14,\"views\":76834,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-11T10:30:04.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ZeroZ_JQ/status/2042913064258015634\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@RushBManager\",\"name\":\"Rush B: Esports Manager | Wishlist now\",\"text\":\"Like Football Manager for Counter-Strike esports.\\n\\nScout talent, build rosters, handle budgets, win majors.\\nMaximum depth, maximum control!\\n\\nWishlist on Steam\",\"likes\":0,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":0,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/RushBManager/status/2042875171938201762/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@li9292\",\"name\":\"李韭二\",\"text\":\"我永远相信openrouter的token数据\\n自媒体也许是噪音\\n但token是真相\",\"likes\":15,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":3,\"views\":4134,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T14:53:28.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/li9292/status/2043341739705172073\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@siantgirl\",\"name\":\"Ryo\",\"text\":\"新公司AI 费用一分都不会报销的，很好，你们报销每月200的都羡慕了\",\"likes\":22,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":13,\"views\":3374,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:51:01.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/siantgirl/status/2043597812479541667\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@KengGuangLong\",\"name\":\"loonggg\",\"text\":\"分享一个特别牛逼的 Skill ，叫：Markdown Viewer Skill 。\\n\\n这个 Skill 里包含了一百多个图例，6000 多精选矢量图标，一句话就可以根据你的 Markdown 内容自动定制各种图表和配图。\\n\\n使用方式就是：把你的 MarkDown 文件让给 Claude Code 这类工具，然后说：充分了解这个 Skills\",\"likes\":968,\"retweets\":187,\"replies\":4,\"views\":68161,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T04:23:04.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/KengGuangLong/status/2043183094061252801\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@ionleu\",\"name\":\"John\",\"text\":\"drop ur startup link\",\"likes\":140,\"retweets\":6,\"replies\":414,\"views\":15302,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T11:24:54.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ionleu/status/2043289250557239449\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@geekbb\",\"name\":\"Geek\",\"text\":\"其实我在很早期就部署过 Hermes，那时候它刚出来。所有好玩的新项目我都会去试一遍，尤其是在找 OpenClaw 的轻量替代时。当时我发现 Hermes 对话里会调用一堆工具，作为小白根本看不懂，就直接关掉删除 pass 了。毕竟自己都看不明白，又怎么可能推荐给兄弟们。\",\"likes\":74,\"retweets\":5,\"replies\":25,\"views\":25710,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T15:06:22.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/geekbb/status/2043344983026225305\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@TheRegister\",\"name\":\"The Register\",\"text\":\"The great virtualization reset: Why HPE has the only real plan B.\\n\\nHow to stay stable when the market shifts around you.\",\"likes\":4028,\"retweets\":304,\"replies\":0,\"views\":23971914,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/TheRegister/status/1990484711299559430/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@elonmusk\",\"name\":\"Elon Musk\",\"text\":\"Starlink gives you fast Internet anywhere on Earth\",\"likes\":37446,\"retweets\":4162,\"replies\":6789,\"views\":12508937,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T20:22:29.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/2043424536927072561\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@9hills\",\"name\":\"九原客\",\"text\":\"最近几天玩 pi 玩的很开心，还是那么喜欢折腾工具。\\n\\n主要是扩展好玩，想怎么定制就怎么定制，而且可以Vibe 扩展。有 ArchLinux 的那种感觉了。\\n\\n刚刚完成一个并行的讲义审核任务，高效～\",\"likes\":35,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":8,\"views\":5824,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:57:39.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/9hills/status/2043569281988972970\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dingyi\",\"name\":\"Ding\",\"text\":\"Fuck I'm done, no more coding agents...\",\"likes\":159,\"retweets\":15,\"replies\":43,\"views\":121839,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T12:59:04.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dingyi/status/2043312948786139528\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@fkysly\",\"name\":\"马天翼\",\"text\":\"CLAUDE OPUS 4.6 被测试证明降智了\\n\\n上周 Claude Opus 4.6 在 BridgeBench 的幻觉基准测试中排名第 2，准确率达 83.3%。\\n\\n今天 Claude Opus 4.6 重新测试后，在排行榜上跌至第 10，准确率仅 68.3%。\\n\\n可以确认 Claude Opus 4.6 的推理水平降低，确实被削弱了。\",\"likes\":79,\"retweets\":10,\"replies\":8,\"views\":19769,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T16:27:07.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/fkysly/status/2043365304148128220\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@MrLarus\",\"name\":\"Larus Canus\",\"text\":\"今天我在对比 Hermes 和 OpenClaw 的帖子里提了点使用感受，没想到 \\n@NousResearch\\n 很快就回复了！\\n\\n他们直接说可以自定义tool call输出，正在开发独立配置和web dashboard，很棒！\\n\\n作为开源项目，团队这么积极回应用户反馈，太有诚意了！继续加油\",\"likes\":28,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":3,\"views\":6782,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T15:00:34.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/MrLarus/status/2043343523743744167\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@KaiXCreator\",\"name\":\"Kaito\",\"text\":\"Which IDE is best for beginners:\\n\\n1) VS Code\\n2) Cursor\\n3) Antigravity\\n4) Claude Code\",\"likes\":45,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":54,\"views\":2100,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:10:28.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/KaiXCreator/status/2043542309313396908\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@lxfater\",\"name\":\"铁锤人\",\"text\":\"Linus 正式认可大家用AI给内核写代码\\n\\n前提是人类必须复杂Review代码\\n\\n标志性事件！！！\",\"likes\":239,\"retweets\":31,\"replies\":9,\"views\":36444,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T23:32:02.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/lxfater/status/2043472240705216571\",\"external_links\":[\"linux/Documentation/process/coding-assistants.rst at master · torvalds/linux\",\"来自 github.com\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@kevinma_dev_zh\",\"name\":\"Kevin Ma\",\"text\":\"即刻是不是凉了，感觉上面都没什么人\",\"likes\":6,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":6,\"views\":12739,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T12:08:33.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/kevinma_dev_zh/status/2043300236916101547\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@CoinBridge_US\",\"name\":\"CoinBridge\",\"text\":\"Turn your real asset into institutional-grade digital securities. Win $600K in free services. Access 400+ global institutions. Only 3 winners selected. Scan QR Code to Apply! \\nDeadline: May 10. Don't miss your spot!\",\"likes\":93,\"retweets\":12,\"replies\":1,\"views\":2604699,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/CoinBridge_US/status/2042656371552784533/photo/1\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@SuisPasDaVinci\",\"name\":\"达芬七\",\"text\":\"说个暴论，\\n会在PC上用AI的人，\\n和只在手机上用AI的人，\\n已经有个非常大的AI信息差鸿沟了。\",\"likes\":924,\"retweets\":37,\"replies\":198,\"views\":517978,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T01:20:45.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/SuisPasDaVinci/status/2043137213202944207\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dashen_wang\",\"name\":\"AI最严厉的父亲\",\"text\":\"ChatGPT Claude Gemini 御三家全都降智\",\"likes\":4,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":635,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T08:42:29.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dashen_wang/status/2043610764507037826\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@NousResearch\",\"name\":\"Nous Research\",\"text\":\"Hermes Agent is an overnight success nine months in the making\",\"likes\":1484,\"retweets\":78,\"replies\":83,\"views\":124758,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T07:40:34.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/NousResearch/status/2043232796366291415\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@imwsl90\",\"name\":\"卫斯理\",\"text\":\"刚看到一个人讲按照 X 收益，如果你做到 1000 刀每月，那就是顶流了\\n\\n这是我目前的收益\\n\\n只是不太懂，我这点流量就算顶流？\\n\\n那 X 中文圈的确很小\",\"likes\":31,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":23,\"views\":5203,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T01:58:06.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/imwsl90/status/2043508998696243648\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@wsl8297\",\"name\":\"Joruno\",\"text\":\"也不知道这股莫名的优越感从哪儿冒出来的。\\n\\n用上 Gmail 就开始嫌弃别人还在用 QQ 邮箱\\n\\n摸两天 React 就拿 Vue 开涮，说什么“只有国人爱用”\\n\\n记住几条 Linux 命令就瞧不起点鼠标的\\n\\n刚把 Docker 跑起来就把本地脚本当成上古遗迹\\n\\n换了 Mac 就在心里把 Windows 贴上“低端”的标签\",\"likes\":112,\"retweets\":17,\"replies\":42,\"views\":16288,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T01:01:05.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/wsl8297/status/2043494651689365714\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@DanKulkov\",\"name\":\"Dan Kulkov\",\"text\":\"claude code not working in \\n\\nso i just stared at laptop for a photo\",\"likes\":432,\"retweets\":26,\"replies\":124,\"views\":28483,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:27:09.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/DanKulkov/status/2043546509359382681\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@brad_zhang2024\",\"name\":\"烟花老师\",\"text\":\"谢谢大家的认可与反馈，迅速更新了第三版，这一版已经很稳定了，我比较满意。\\n  强烈推荐大家升级到这一版！\\n(附件7 张图是最新效果)\\n\\n  收到了很多小伙伴的反馈，其中 codex 兼容和出图不稳定是最多的。\\n\\n  所以认真解决了“怎么稳定产出样图级技术图”这件事。\\n  这七张最新的图片均是由 codex 生成\",\"likes\":242,\"retweets\":48,\"replies\":12,\"views\":26194,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:38:43.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/brad_zhang2024/status/2043322925072388408\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@noahduck283\",\"name\":\"诺鸭船长3\",\"text\":\"刚刚和一位有两栋楼的巨佬聊天\\n\\n他透露：\\n\\n1.抖音基本可以放弃创作 除非你在维护个人品牌\\n\\n2.创作成本远远大于回报\\n\\n3.推特1万粉的商业价值大于抖音100万粉\\n\\n4.全力干X就完了\\n\\n跟对人，做对事\",\"likes\":592,\"retweets\":49,\"replies\":101,\"views\":133003,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T07:02:12.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/noahduck283/status/2043223138977321296\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@kapilansh_twt\",\"name\":\"kapilansh\",\"text\":\"OpenClaw had the most hype\\nand the shortest lifespan\\nof any AI tool in 2026\\n\\nhere today\\ngone before anyone wrote a tutorial\\n\\ndid anyone actually use it\\nor were we all just watching the hype\",\"likes\":90,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":85,\"views\":4071,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:37:23.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/kapilansh_twt/status/2043564182751342883\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@ListingHelp_UK\",\"name\":\"Listing.Help\",\"text\":\"A full-cycle successful listing of your project on top crypto exchanges!\",\"likes\":416,\"retweets\":47,\"replies\":17,\"views\":8240731,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ListingHelp_UK/status/1969067248343196012/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@bridgemindai\",\"name\":\"BridgeMind\",\"text\":\"CLAUDE OPUS 4.6 IS NERFED.\\n\\nBridgeBench just proved it.\\n\\nLast week Claude Opus 4.6 ranked #2 on the Hallucination benchmark with an accuracy of 83.3%.\\n\\nToday Claude Opus 4.6 was retested and it fell to #10 on the leaderboard with an accuracy of only 68.3%.\\n\\nA 98% increase in\",\"likes\":6245,\"retweets\":925,\"replies\":436,\"views\":832609,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:32:11.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/bridgemindai/status/2043321284113670594\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@1Umairshaikh\",\"name\":\"Umair Shaikh\",\"text\":\"Let's end this debate \\n\\n-Claude\\n-Codex\\n\\nWhich one is better?\",\"likes\":19,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":21,\"views\":549,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T08:39:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/1Umairshaikh/status/2043609886689521926\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@0xAllen\",\"name\":\"0xAllen\",\"text\":\"Hermes Agent 最被低估的不是模型，是那个 .env 文件。今天把最近总结的 5 个技巧一次性交出来。\\n\\n文中不涉及过多操作教程，谨慎阅读！\\n\\n一、主模型 & 备模型\\n\\nHermes 在 Token\",\"likes\":70,\"retweets\":10,\"replies\":22,\"views\":8952,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:11:27.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/0xAllen/status/2043542558996074773\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@oran_ge\",\"name\":\"Orange AI\",\"text\":\"其实从来都是这样的：\\n人人都是产品经理，产品不再稀缺\\n人人都能开发软件，软件一文不值\\n人人都能生成视频，短片价值暴跌\\n经济学的基本原理建立在「商品稀缺」的假设上\\n人类因为稀缺性而交易，稀缺就代表了价值\\n当整个比特世界都不再是稀缺\\n那人类就会找到新的稀缺\",\"likes\":51,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":7,\"views\":10299,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T23:08:33.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/oran_ge/status/2043466328913461364\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@RealHanyaHu\",\"name\":\"Hanya Hu\",\"text\":\"我已经不焦虑了\\n\\nAI时代，正如\\n@lanhubiji\\n 所说的路就三条：躺平、OPC、修行。\\n\\nOPC是另一种形式的打工、陪跑、做嫁衣，用自己的时间帮别人的梦想续命。修行，是把自己当成一个项目来经营。\\n我在OPC里转了很长时间。最近基本放手了。\\n\\n我还不想彻底躺平。\\n\\n外面燥音太多。硅谷尤其如此。\",\"likes\":40,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":13,\"views\":4227,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T15:53:26.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/RealHanyaHu/status/2043356830425116747\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@m0d8ye\",\"name\":\"Max Lv\",\"text\":\"最近的一点小心得\",\"likes\":427,\"retweets\":64,\"replies\":16,\"views\":50991,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T08:18:44.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/m0d8ye/status/2043242401041703222\",\"external_links\":[\"maxlv.net用 Claude Code 将三万行 Go 项目移植到 Rust：Agent Team 实践与 Harness 效率优化以 mihomo（Clash Meta）代理内核的 Rust 移植为案例，分享使用 Claude Code Agent Team 进行大型项目移植的完整实践——从角色分工、里程碑规划到 CLAUDE.md 与 Memory 系统的效率调优。\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@plantegg\",\"name\":\"plantegg\",\"text\":\"太狠了，即使我这样的Claude粉丝也不会这么夸张：\\n建议朋友们无论用任何方法，一定要不择手段地、不择手段地、不择手段地，搞一个claude账号 + 一个gemini账号\\n\\n然后让自己的大部分信息输入和信息输出都依靠这两个东西\",\"likes\":59,\"retweets\":6,\"replies\":15,\"views\":22269,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T23:25:48.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/plantegg/status/2043470670076707131\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dearemon\",\"name\":\"禿道道\",\"text\":\"请不要在app上给我推荐“你可能认识的人”\\n\\n是的，我是认识他们，但我不喜欢他们\\n\\n产品经理怎么不猜猜，既然我们这么大概率认识，那又为什么不是好友呢？\\n\\n希望各大厂的产品经理能够看到。\",\"likes\":591,\"retweets\":37,\"replies\":27,\"views\":18111,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T03:55:08.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dearemon/status/2043176064147660949\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Vtrivedy10\",\"name\":\"Viv\",\"text\":\"Harness, Memory, Context Fragments, & the Bitter Lesson\\n\\nthis is a work in progress mental dump on interesting intersections between how we use and design a harness, implications for memory being accumulated over long timescales, and the search bitter lesson we can’t escape\\n\\nthis\",\"likes\":997,\"retweets\":129,\"replies\":36,\"views\":49483,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T20:35:55.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Vtrivedy10/status/2043427918127513836\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Pillievers\",\"name\":\"PillNet AI\",\"text\":\"The Wallets Nobody Can Save. The Quantum Problem All Chains Should Be Scared About.\\n\\nGoogle just told the world it has until 2029 to go quantum safe. We’re in 2026. That’s three years. Ethereum’s plan requires four hard forks spread over years, realistically putting them at 2030\",\"likes\":5489,\"retweets\":471,\"replies\":88,\"views\":6369253,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Pillievers/status/2041779746535551448/photo/1\",