n\\n手握3780亿美元年交易额，560万个店铺，Shopify把整个后台的读写权限，全开放给了所有AI Agent， 产品、订单、库存、SEO、图片，想改什么改什么。\",\"likes\":2760,\"retweets\":478,\"replies\":61,\"views\":728703,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-11T14:16:44.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/AYi_AInotes/status/2042970104921542896\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@nash_su\",\"name\":\"nash_su - e/acc\",\"text\":\"llm-wiki v0.3.0 版本更新发布啦 \\n\\n新增检索优化，搜索问答更加准确：\\n  - 检索增强：BM25 + 意图分类 + RRF 融合（benchmark 验证）+ 向量搜索（benchmark: 58.2% → 71.4% recall）\\n  - LanceDB 向量存储后端\\n\\n文件夹导入，批量导入更加方便：\\n  - 文件夹递归导入 + 保留目录结构\\n  -\",\"likes\":326,\"retweets\":58,\"replies\":20,\"views\":31638,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T08:31:54.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/nash_su/status/2043245715309412526\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@RealHanyaHu\",\"name\":\"Hanya Hu\",\"text\":\"为了用好Claude\\n决定买个MacBook pro 48gb memory \\n理由很充分是不\",\"likes\":52,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":54,\"views\":6469,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T23:25:47.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/RealHanyaHu/status/2043470665551130923\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@huolongguodomgt\",\"name\":\"龙共火火\",\"text\":\"有个朋友做 ai 编程培训，让大家一人创业。他告诉了我一个扎心的事实。 ai 编程真正对产品经理有用，或者是老板群体。但来的 80%都是程序员想要逆天改命。\",\"likes\":62,\"retweets\":7,\"replies\":15,\"views\":18569,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T20:51:47.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/huolongguodomgt/status/2043431911297876361\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@CMGS1988\",\"name\":\"CMGS\",\"text\":\"普通人 Opus4.6 到头了，未来更强的模型肯定是 B 端优先…C 端随着硬件提升只做降本，增智速度一定赶不上 B 端…还真是赛博朋克 2077…\",\"likes\":58,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":7,\"views\":10425,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:04:26.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/CMGS1988/status/2043540791591829534\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@QueerMajority\",\"name\":\"Queer Majority\",\"text\":\"The online kangaroo court of public opinion is where due process and women’s safety go to die. | \\n@CJFerguson1111\",\"likes\":602,\"retweets\":93,\"replies\":33,\"views\":1635402,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/QueerMajority/status/1990954426945974387/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@NousResearch\",\"name\":\"Nous Research\",\"text\":\"Weekends are for hacking!\\n\\nWhat are you building with Hermes?\",\"likes\":596,\"retweets\":24,\"replies\":213,\"views\":54405,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T14:56:09.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/NousResearch/status/2043342414643855806\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dontbesilent\",\"name\":\"dontbesilent\",\"text\":\"本来想做个网站，现在先不做了\\n\\n等这个上线吧\",\"likes\":17,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":1,\"views\":5427,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:58:01.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dontbesilent/status/2043569375819821475\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@PandaTalk8\",\"name\":\"Mr Panda\",\"text\":\"我为什么喜欢 Opus ， 因为我觉得Opus 的AI味儿比 GPT 淡了很多。  这一点上感觉Opus 学的更像我一些。  \\n\\nGPT 更像是一个PUA的高手， 总是喜欢给我讲一些故弄玄虚的话来刺激我。\",\"likes\":14,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":13,\"views\":3750,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T21:10:55.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/PandaTalk8/status/2043436724790137215\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Zesee\",\"name\":\"Rachel\",\"text\":\"一人公司必备\\n如何一键拥有130个AI数字员工\\n\\ngithub：agency-agents\",\"likes\":17,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":3,\"views\":1795,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:17:16.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Zesee/status/2043589320787812505\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@yhslgg\",\"name\":\"老杨啊\",\"text\":\"最近AI脱口秀的流量是真猛呀，\\n一个号7天就干到了14.3万粉；\\n我自己在视频号小试了一下2天1500粉，小爆了一个视频涨了1300粉。\\n继续测试一周，看看效果。\",\"likes\":292,\"retweets\":39,\"replies\":71,\"views\":64561,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T02:58:32.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/yhslgg/status/2043524205908742279\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@lidangzzz\",\"name\":\"lidang 立党 （全网劝人卖房、劝人学CS、劝人买SP500和NASDAQ100第一人）\",\"text\":\"Goal Driven\\nGoal Driven\\nGoal Driven\\n\\n什么时候你们才能在github上点个star并且goal driven的模式，我真求求你们了\\n\\n\\nhttps://\\ngithub.com/lidangzzz/goal\\n-driven/\\n…\\n\\n设定一个subagent，朝着goal（目标）不断工作，\\n\\n设定一个master agent，设定一个goal完成的criteria（判据），让master agent定期检查subagent的工作，\",\"likes\":48,\"retweets\":8,\"replies\":5,\"views\":29333,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T20:24:14.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/lidangzzz/status/2043424980055282163\",\"external_links\":[\"https://github.com/lidangzzz/goal-driven/…\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@0xjiawei\",\"name\":\"Jiawei\",\"text\":\"周末用 \\n@NousResearch\\n Hermes 和 \\n@XiaomiMiMo\\n 做了高强度研究。一开始是让 GPT 5.4 写骨架，我修改内容，再让 Mimo V2 Pro 做一轮 review，修改内容和润色中文的表达流畅度。\\n\\n用着用着就跳过 GPT 直接用 Mimo 写了。\\n\\n1. GPT\",\"likes\":17,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":2,\"views\":3651,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T01:46:55.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/0xjiawei/status/2043506184750248126\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@rezoundous\",\"name\":\"Tyler\",\"text\":\"Can't believe I'm saying this, but now...\\n\\n$20 Codex = $20 Claude\",\"likes\":1095,\"retweets\":36,\"replies\":104,\"views\":118218,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T12:25:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/rezoundous/status/2043304374492164219\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@oran_ge\",\"name\":\"Orange AI\",\"text\":\"对最近的 AI 文章都很烦了\\n天天什么纺织工人，什么银行柜员\\n所有人都在举这些过去的老掉牙的例子\\n还不是自己看书得到的，是 AI 给出的例子\\n真的服了\\n这难道是 AI 给人类软性洗脑的一种方式？\",\"likes\":25,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":10,\"views\":9086,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T23:51:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ora