 a\",\"likes\":1700,\"retweets\":159,\"replies\":121,\"views\":293960,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T03:34:16.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/chatgpt21/status/2043170812484608509\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@alexwtlf\",\"name\":\"Alex Ibragimov\",\"text\":\"Who will win the AI race and reach AGI first?\",\"likes\":33,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":50,\"views\":1344,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:57:29.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/alexwtlf/status/2043569240154767853\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@himself65\",\"name\":\"Bread\",\"text\":\"haiku 短诗\\nsonnet 十四行诗\\nopus 杰作\\nmythos 神话\\n下一个模型叫：永乐大典\",\"likes\":695,\"retweets\":29,\"replies\":48,\"views\":66745,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-11T20:41:05.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/himself65/status/2043066830781321726\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@uge198568\",\"name\":\"U哥\",\"text\":\"你们真的信我一下，把现在AI脱口秀的那些爆粉账号ID都记录一下，我们3个月后，不，可能1个月后，你看看还有几家在更新的。\\n2026年4月13日\\n但你想做，我依然建议你试试，在做一个项目的过程中得到的能力积累，很重要。\\n但你已经有这种能力了，那就别浪费生命了\\n聪明人找杠杆，做复利\\n蠢人找捷径，玩归零\",\"likes\":12,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":3,\"views\":770,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:41:33.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/uge198568/status/2043595431754789328\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@wolfyxbt\",\"name\":\"杀破狼 WolfyXBT\",\"text\":\"笑死，交易所老板都在吵架，孙哥非常努力地在 Build 他的白 AI\\n\\n\\nhttp://\\nB.AI 这个域名我记得是孙哥上个月买的，这个域名应该是花了不少钱，刚刚点进去看了一下，孙哥把各种主流的模型都接到了一起，包括 MiniMax、Kimi、GLM、GPT、Claude、Gemini 等等等等，用户可以按需选择。\",\"likes\":261,\"retweets\":30,\"replies\":129,\"views\":214817,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:38:09.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/wolfyxbt/status/2043322784642982277\",\"external_links\":[\"http://B.AI\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@anorth_chen\",\"name\":\"North@CreaoAI\",\"text\":\"Karpathy 的这条推文，非常准确地描述了当下市场里，用户对 AI 产品认知正在发生的割裂，而且这个裂口还在不断扩大。\\n\\n我最近一段时间在市场里的观察对这个现象也同样感同身受。\\n\\n非常多的人，对 AI 的理解依然停留在免费版 ChatGPT——一种“更聪明一点的智力问答工具”。\\n\\n但即便是已经用过 agent\",\"likes\":7,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":1,\"views\":494,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:20:24.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/anorth_chen/status/2043544810246803641\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@cybrid_xyz\",\"name\":\"Cybrid Technology Inc\",\"text\":\"Connect your remittance app to US-based users and expand globally. \\n\\nCybrid’s API unlocks stablecoin-powered corridors for seamless international transfers.\",\"likes\":23345,\"retweets\":1802,\"replies\":0,\"views\":164825713,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/cybrid_xyz/status/1983542576985919595/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@lifesinger\",\"name\":\"Frank Wang 玉伯\",\"text\":\"Ivan \\n@ivanhzhao\\n says agency is a muscle. I'd push back on that.\\n\\nA muscle can atrophy. A muscle can be replaced. AI is already the strongest muscle in the room — it writes faster, designs faster, analyzes faster than any human.\\n\\nIf agency were just a muscle, AI would have already\",\"likes\":9,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":4,\"views\":3760,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T15:31:11.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/lifesinger/status/2043351230156771762\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@MiniMax_AI\",\"name\":\"MiniMax (official)\",\"text\":\"We're delighted to announce that MiniMax M2.7 is now officially open source. \\nWith SOTA performance in SWE-Pro (56.22%) and Terminal Bench 2 (57.0%).\\n\\nYou can find it on Hugging Face now. Enjoy!\\nhuggingface：\\nhttps://\\nhuggingface.co/MiniMaxAI/Mini\\nMax-M2.7\\n…\\nBlog: \\nhttps://\\nminimax.io/news/minimax-m\\n27-en\\n…\\nMiniMax API:\",\"likes\":5406,\"retweets\":1008,\"replies\":267,\"views\":1405395,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T01:00:14.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/MiniMax_AI/status/2043132047397659000\",\"external_links\":[\"https://huggingface.co/MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2.7…\",\"https://minimax.io/news/minimax-m27-en…\",\"huggingface.co/MiniMaxAI/Mini…\",\"opensource.org/osd\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@Sumanth_077\",\"name\":\"Sumanth\",\"text\":\"The self-improving AI agent from Nous Research!\\n\\nHermes Agent is a self-improving AI agent that builds skills from your work, improves them over time, and remembers across sessions.\\n\\nMost AI agents reset every conversation. You teach them your codebase structure, they forget. You\",\"likes\":59,\"retweets\":17,\"replies\":7,\"views\":4312,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T12:21:05.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Sumanth_077/status/2043303391628337479\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@akshay_pachaar\",\"name\":\"Akshay\",\"text\":\"A single 𝗖𝗟𝗔𝗨𝗗𝗘.𝗺𝗱 file just hit 15K GitHub stars.\\n\\n(derived from Karpathy's coding rules)\\n\\nAndrej Karpathy observed that LLMs make the same predictable mistakes when writing code: over-engineering, ignoring existing patterns, and adding dependencies you never asked for.\",\"likes\":4227,\"retweets\":359,\"replies\":50,\"views\":334376,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T17:02:34.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/akshay_pachaar/status/2043374229199151351\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@LunaAI519\",\"name\":\"Luna\",\"text\":\"如果你的程序员老公\\n\\n下班回家只会打游戏\\n\\n全口不提 AI\\n\\n听我一句劝\\n\\n你要考虑一下你俩的未来了\",\"likes\":9,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":10,\"views\":1737,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:06:16.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/LunaAI519/status/2043556351872553268\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@typhooncon\",\"name\":\"TyphoonCon\",\"text\":\"TyphoonCon 2026 trainings are live.\\nLearn directly from top researchers: from exploitation and fuzzing to reverse engineering and modern vuln research.\\n\\nSmall groups. Real techniques. Immediate impact. \\nSeats are limited! Secure your spot today.\",\"likes\":0,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":0,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/typhooncon/status/2040837188946923716/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@elliotchen100\",\"name\":\"艾略特\",\"text\":\"讲真，我们没有想到 Memory Sparse Attention 的 GitHub Repo 会这么快到 3000 星。更没有想到大家的关注度这么高。也许真的印证了那句话吧，「能带走的才是记忆，带不走的则是过去」。\\n\\n起初，MSA 只是一篇论文。一个支持 1 亿 Token 上下文的端到端方案，大胆，也优雅。\\n\\n核心就两个点：一个是 Dual\",\"likes\":73,\"retweets\":10,\"replies\":8,\"views\":8768,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T09:12:27.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/elliotchen100/status/2043255919409254865\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@jinchenma_ai\",\"name\":\"金尘马\",\"text\":\"一个月前，跟风买 Mac Mini 的朋友\\n\\n现在你的 Mac Mini 怎么样了？\\n\\n爽用中？吃灰了？还是准备咸鱼二手了？\",\"likes\":22,\"retweets\":3,\"replies\":22,\"views\":7901,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:17:48.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/jinchenma_ai/status/2043559255362736435\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@berryxia\",\"name\":\"Berryxia.AI\",\"text\":\"兄弟们，Claude Code 终于有「全代码库视觉地图」了！\\n\\n全新开源工具 Code-review-graph直接本地生成项目完整关系图：\\n\\n 100% 本地运行，零云端  \\n 自动映射整个仓库文件依赖  \\n Claude 瞬间看懂每个文件怎么连在一起  \\n 大幅减少 hallucination，上下文精准到爆\",\"likes\":740,\"retweets\":127,\"replies\":13,\"views\":44341,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-11T22:15:05.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/berryxia/status/2043090485967987117\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@KaiXCreator\",\"name\":\"Kaito\",\"text\":\"Honestly, which ecosystem do you enjoy using the most?\",\"likes\":26,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":19,\"views\":1149,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T16:10:47.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/KaiXCreator/status/2043361195676332154\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promot