36634093845/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@chetaslua\",\"name\":\"Chetaslua\",\"text\":\"Mythos vs GPT-5.4 Pro\\n\\n> mythos mogs it , and dont take an hour for every questions \\n\\n> Mythos can actually reason over million-token inputs while GPT-5.4 basically falls apart at that scale\\n\\n>Mythos actually do abetter developer's job on unfamiliar code compared to 5.4 pro\",\"likes\":434,\"retweets\":34,\"replies\":59,\"views\":50807,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T15:38:21.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/chetaslua/status/2043353033283878990\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@anorth_chen\",\"name\":\"North@CreaoAI\",\"text\":\"关于Evie提到的第三点和第五点，我有些自己从时代背景下观察到的看法\\n\\n互联网行业的发展和竞争重心经历过几个阶段，每个阶段都是由行业供给侧主导的变化。\\n\\n最开始程序员稀缺，所以强调“技术”，因为市面上主流需求尚未被满足，你只要有程序员能做出来，产品就不愁卖。\",\"likes\":4,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":392,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T08:30:30.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/anorth_chen/status/2043607748504666423\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@supezen\",\"name\":\"ZEN\",\"text\":\"让 CC 稳定不降智的小技巧\",\"likes\":75,\"retweets\":14,\"replies\":6,\"views\":11699,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:46:37.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/supezen/status/2043551405328461868\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@orhundev\",\"name\":\"Orhun Parmaksız\",\"text\":\"man, I love terminal spinners\\n\\n\\nhttps://\\ngithub.com/vyfor/rattles\\n\\n#rustlang #ratatui\",\"likes\":3760,\"retweets\":257,\"replies\":34,\"views\":122632,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-11T13:33:33.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/orhundev/status/2042959236586418652\",\"external_links\":[\"https://github.com/vyfor/rattles\"],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@imwsl90\",\"name\":\"卫斯理\",\"text\":\"coding plan lite停止续费通知……\\n\\n一句话\\n\\n“玩不起就不要玩”\\n\\n在做这个活动的时候没做