ce in Japan\\n\\nRead about Chelsea's experience - and how you can do it too\",\"likes\":0,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":0,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/travellemming/status/1956413605076689355/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@NFTCPS\",\"name\":\"鸟哥 | 蓝鸟会\",\"text\":\"一个桌面客户端，把 AI 对话、Agent 模式、本地 RAG、API 网关全塞进去了。\\n\\nAQBot，Rust + Tauri 写的，跨平台，轻量，数据全在本地。\\n\\n这东西能干嘛：\\n\\n对话层面——\\n- OpenAI、Claude、Gemini 随便切，支持 OpenAI 兼容接口\\n- 多 Key 轮换负载均衡，再也不怕单个 Key 限速\\n-\",\"likes\":77,\"retweets\":10,\"replies\":2,\"views\":9743,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T11:23:54.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/NFTCPS/status/2043288999410987448\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@penny777\",\"name\":\"Penny777\",\"text\":\"分享一个 Cloudflare 官方的免费「梯子」 \\n\\n这几天折腾网络简直燃尽了，有时候 API 可以连上，但是用的软件，例如 Conductor 这种，又连不上了，跑个 AI 太难了…\\n\\n折腾的过程中发现 Cloudflare Warp 居然都能连，而且还免费，不限流。缺点就是：容易偶尔断开，以及有的网站加载很慢。\",\"likes\":11,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":9,\"views\":1074,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T08:22:11.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/penny777/status/2043605656620708121\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dearemon\",\"name\":\"禿道道\",\"text\":\"如果一个程序员跟你说\\n“这个 bug 一小时能修好。”\\n你应该相信他，\\n\\n而不是每隔三个小时去问一次进度\",\"likes\":326,\"retweets\":14,\"replies\":29,\"views\":36526,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T05:03:11.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dearemon/status/2043555577192956132\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@YuLin807\",\"name\":\"QingYue\",\"text\":\"opus 4.6 降智太狠 /model claude-opus-4-5 切换到4.5 用\",\"likes\":8,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":2,\"views\":1316,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T18:05:52.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/YuLin807/status/2043390158347850049\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@axiaisacat\",\"name\":\"axiaisacat\"