name\":\"Geek\",\"text\":\"不要啰嗦，让任何 LLM 说人话。不废话, 不客套, 直接给答案。\\n\\n一段 system prompt 把 LLM 啰嗦的、AI 客服腔的输出变成直接、有信息量的回答。适用于任何模型 (GPT, Gemini, LLaMA 等)。在 GPT-4o-mini 上测试 减少 73% 输出长度, GPT-5.4 上 减少 72%, 同时保留所有有用信息。\",\"likes\":96,\"retweets\":8,\"replies\":7,\"views\":14287,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T04:40:44.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/geekbb/status/2043549928379842677\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@gabrielchua\",\"name\":\"Gabriel Chua\",\"text\":\"Here’s how we use Codex to:\\n\\n> understand large codebases\\n> review PRs faster\\n> build macOS apps\\n> turn Figma into code\\n> automate bug triage\\n> create a CLI as agent tools\\n> analyze datasets\\n> generate slide decks\\n> coordinate new-hire onboarding\\n> learn a new concept\\n\\n…and\",\"likes\":747,\"retweets\":65,\"replies\":19,\"views\":43375,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T14:43:11.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/gabrielchua/status/2043339151278506234\",\"external_links\":[\"Codex use cases\",\"来自 developers.openai.com\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@skywind3000\",\"name\":\"LIN WEI\",\"text\":\"准备蒸馏我自己了，别说总结的还挺准：\",\"likes\":34,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":9,\"views\":9675,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:19:16.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/skywind3000/status/2043318033838674157\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@DRbitcoin36\",\"name\":\"比特欧 Elvin\",\"text\":\"回到三年前，你会更愿意在哪个平台做自媒体\\n只可以选其中两个\",\"likes\":98,\"retweets\":7,\"replies\":65,\"views\":121533,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T10:27:17.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/DRbitcoin36/status/2043274748948611556\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@whatRanjuSaid\",\"name\":\"Ranju\",\"text\":\"just got my MacBook Pro, what should I install\",\"likes\":2522,\"retweets\":103,\"replies\":359,\"views\":154038,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T19:07:38.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/whatRanjuSaid/status/2043405700630560834\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dashen_wang\",\"name\":\"AI最严厉的父亲\",\"text\":\"帮朋友把 Toonflow 部署好了。 \\n\\n一款把小说直接打成 AI 短剧 / 漫剧的全流程工厂。\\n\\n从事件图谱抽取、剧本改编、分镜生成，到图片视频一键出片， 三层 Agent 协作、无限画布、可编程供应商，全都给你安排得明明白白。\\n\\n朋友象征性塞了我 999， 我象征性假装推辞了三秒钟。\",\"likes\":507,\"retweets\":98,\"replies\":6,\"views\":33044,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T04:03:05.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dashen_wang/status/2043178064478441646\",\"external_links\":[\"GitHub - HBAI-Ltd/Toonflow-app: Toonflow 是一款 AI 短剧漫剧工具，能够利用 AI 技术将小说自动转化为剧本，并结合 AI 生成的图片和视频，实现高效的...\",\"来自 github.com\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@Easesourcing_\",\"name\":\"Easesourcing\",\"text\":\"Hey there!\\nI’ve set up a group for people in the import/export world to chat, share tips, and help each other with resources. I’ll also be sharing useful updates and tips on foreign trade trends and sourcing strategies in the group.\\nFeel free to check out my profile for the\",\"likes\":275,\"retweets\":61,\"replies\":2,\"views\":3864757,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Easesourcing_/status/2042539038083871013/photo/1\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@LLMJunky\",\"name\":\"am.will\",\"text\":\"Whoa! There's hidden features in the Codex App!\\n\\nAnd you can enable them right now. \\n\\nThere's an inbuilt browser, and you can leave comments directly on specific elements.\\n\\nI'm normally on top of these things, now I'm wondering what else they're hiding in there \\n\\nSee Max's post\",\"likes\":290,\"retweets\":28,\"replies\":21,\"views\":27374,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T06:57:13.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/LLMJunky/status/2043584274796880197\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@TaNGSoFT\",\"name\":\"𝙩𝙮≃𝙛{𝕩}^A𝕀²·ℙarad𝕚g𝕞\",\"text\":\"早就说过了，openclaw只是LLM交互loop内核的一个发行版，类似Linux的Ubuntu，各种发行版多了去了，核心还是kernel！\\n\\n\\nhttp://\\npi.dev，claude code sdk，或者Hermes agent用的是啥内核？\",\"likes\":7,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":0,\"views\":1916,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T11:53:01.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/TaNGSoFT/status/2043296324515467509\",\"external_links\":[\"http://pi.dev\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@JoyLi629\",\"name\":\"Joey Lee\",\"text\":\"Harness 插件化可能是今年开源 agent 生态最重要的一步。\\n\\n\\n@steipete\\n 放出 OpenClaw 下一版两个实验：\\n• Strict mode — 强制 GPT-5.x 不偷懒\\n• Harness 插件化 — Anthropic SDK、Codex 一行配置热替换\\n\\n很多人关注 strict mode，但 harness 插件化才是杀手锏。\",\"likes\":7,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":1,\"views\":2771,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T10:58:20.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/JoyLi629/status/2043282566929584544\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@msjiaozhu\",\"name\":\"MapleShaw\",\"text\":\"Harness Engineering 这个概念太火了\\n\\n刚好最近开始高强度用 Claude Code，借着这套最佳实践好好体验了这个概念背后的意义，既解决了 Claude Code 的“不听话”，确实也让输出更工程化。\\n\\n建议直接把仓库的 .claude 目录整个扔进项目，然后直接敲 /weather-orchestrator，感受下 Claude 自己把\",\"likes\":17,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":3,\"views\":1765,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T01:56:33.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/msjiaozhu/status/2043508609200607736\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@thsottiaux\",\"name\":\"Tibo\",\"text\":\"Codex App has achieved take-off internally. I can hear the fans\",\"likes\":2098,\"retweets\":99,\"replies\":218,\"views\":128183,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T02:31:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/thsottiaux/status/2043517277455491430\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@wangdefou\",\"name\":\"得否\",\"text\":\"最近一段时间都在忙于筹备活动\\n这玩意儿真的太耗费心神了\\n下次再也不搞免费的活动了，太磨人了\",\"likes\":6,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":3,\"views\":268,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T09:04:08.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/wangdefou/status/2043616212459069885\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false