，导致下次启动不了\\n\\n2. 让Hermes gateway run自动启动\",\"likes\":9,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":2320,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T03:48:03.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/manateelazycat/status/2043536668469379477\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Viraelelyon\",\"name\":\"三文魚夢女\",\"text\":\"卧槽Claude我爱你\",\"likes\":188,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":10,\"views\":33840,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T14:58:03.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Viraelelyon/status/2043342889565208711\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@PandaTalk8\",\"name\":\"Mr Panda\",\"text\":\"垃圾\",\"likes\":33,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":27,\"views\":12450,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T10:15:27.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/PandaTalk8/status/2043271773635178772\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@ianneo_ai\",\"name\":\"Ian (伊恩)\",\"text\":\"AI coding 继续吃掉一部分前端外包\\n\\n这个开源项目有点狠啊\\n\\n给它一个网址，跑一下，它会自己截图、扒设计 token、拆组件 spec、下载资源，还原成 Next.js 项目\\n\\n重点不是仿站\\n\\n重点是把看懂一个网站变成直接拿到一套可维护代码\\n\\n重建旧站、找回丢失源码、拆高手页面，这类工作流会越来越猛！\",\"likes\":73,\"retweets\":14,\"replies\":4,\"views\":35045,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T11:30:42.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/ianneo_ai/status/2043290711660081501\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@CreaoAI\",\"name\":\"Creao AI\",\"text\":\"Two weeks of the new CREAO. We've shown you 11 features, all working together:  \\n\\nWeek 1 — Foundations: \\n→ Save any conversation as a reusable agent \\n→ Watch outputs build live in file preview \\n→ MAX Thinking — when tasks get harder, your agent thinks harder \\n→ Agent Files —\",\"likes\":12,\"retweets\":6,\"replies\":2,\"views\":229,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T17:46:01.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/CreaoAI/status/2043385161174454674\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@yetone\",\"name\":\"yetone\",\"text\":\"昨天在杭州见到了很多推友，开心٩(๑^o^๑)۶\",\"likes\":86,\"retweets\":4,\"replies\":9,\"views\":11088,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T18:22:39.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/yetone/status/2043394381580063108\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dotey\",\"name\":\"宝玉\",\"text\":\"\",\"likes\":847,\"retweets\":214,\"replies\":8,\"views\":73278,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T08:12:00.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dotey/status/2043240706156728322\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dontbesilent\",\"name\":\"dontbesilent\",\"text\":\"“我发现中文内容比英文内容好太多了”\\n\\n围城呀\",\"likes\":77,\"retweets\":4,\"replies\":17,\"views\":11700,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T18:07:12.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dontbesilent/status/2043390493212758397\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@XDCNetwork\",\"name\":\"XDC Network\",\"text\":\"XDC Pulse – March 2026 is Live!\\nMarch brought strong momentum across the XDC ecosystem with key updates in DeFi, real-world assets, and global expansion.\\n\\n- XDC DeFi Accelerator (Plug and Play)\\n- GoodDollar Reserve now live on XDC\\n- AUDDapt grant program integration\\n- Global\",\"likes\":934,\"retweets\":118,\"replies\":16,\"views\":5257140,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/XDCNetwork/status/2042589371057213614/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@0xSero\",\"name\":\"0xSero\",\"text\":\"Defending MiniMax\\n\\nI think it’s fine they set up a license. We kind of deserve it. \\n\\nYou work on something with dozens of people burning through investment money. Put it out to the world for free.\\n\\nPeople say you’re benchmaxxing, call you a communist spy, take your models and\",\"likes\":1135,\"retweets\":64,\"replies\":61,\"views\":44852,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T21:02:55.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/0xSero/status/2043434713826603358\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@shao__meng\",\"name\":\"meng shao\",\"text\":\"Chrome DevTools 做过前端的朋友们肯定都很熟悉，Chrome DevTools MCP 就是给 AI Agent 用的 Chrome DevTools（MCP 必备之一）\\n\\nAI Agent 有了它就可以做我们前端做的这些事了（难怪说前端已死.. 不只是写代码）\\n· 性能工程：Lighthouse 审计、Trace、内存泄漏检测、LCP 优化分析\\n·\",\"likes\":35,\"retweets\":4,\"replies\":3,\"views\":5654,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T00:27:25.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/shao__meng/status/2043486178712916353\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@shisoftgenius\",\"name\":\"Shisoft\",\"text\":\"之前一直以为是流言，直到在 GitHub Copilot 里的 ChatGPT-5.4 看到了这个\",\"likes\":25,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":0,\"views\":9691,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T19:52:50.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/shisoftgenius/status/2043417077894013391\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@elonmusk\",\"name\":\"Elon Musk\",\"text\":\"South Africa won’t allow Starlink to be licensed, even though I was BORN THERE, simply because I am not Black!\\n\\nWe were offered many times the opportunity to bribe our way to a license by pretending that a Black guy runs Starlink SA, but I have refused to do so on principle.\",\"likes\":286179,\"retweets\":52026,\"replies\":22560,\"views\":23115893,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T10:49:13.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/2043280270238101890\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@dontbesilent\",\"name\":\"dontbesilent\",\"text\":\"看了一些所谓有认知的博主和观众的答疑连麦，想吐槽一下\\n\\n当提问的人的问题是：我应该选方向 A 还是方向 B\\n\\n这些 “博主” 总是想要直接去回答这些问题，但实际上选 A 或者选 B 都是错的\\n\\n你犹豫不知道选 A 还是选 B，是因为不了解 A 或 B 的具体信息。没有充分的信息足以让你去决策\",\"likes\":32,\"retweets\":7,\"replies\":9,\"views\":2720,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:06:30.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/dontbesilent/status/2043586609174696163\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@overlayerfi\",\"name\":\"Overlayer\",\"text\":\"Overlayer’s \\n@HackenProof\\n DualDefense contest is now complete.\\n\\n119 hackers. 197 submissions. $6,000 in rewards.\\n\\nThanks to everyone who reviewed the system and pushed the code further. \\n\\nSecurity is not a badge at the end, but a continuous part of building protocol\",\"likes\":19,\"retweets\":2,\"replies\":2,\"views\":473284,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/overlayerfi/status/2042713664076075432/photo/1\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@yanhua1010\",\"name\":\"Yanhua\",\"text\":\"为什么Claude Cowork中的sonnet和opus模型上下文只有200k?\\n\\n才发现Claude Code中也是......，是因为我是Pro订阅的原因吗？\",\"likes\":8,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":12,\"views\":10411,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:37:16.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/2043322560776184268\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@real_kai42\",\"name\":\"Kai\",\"text\":\"跟模型一起做方案设计是真的累，模型对架构的更新速度和理解能力，人是真的赶不上  \\n\\n给我的感觉就是，你让模型帮你做去日本的旅游计划，聊了一小时后，模型问  \\n“东京有三种地铁通票，分别 ABC，优缺点对比如下，你拍板一下选哪个，这样我可以给你的日本交通计划的公交交通部分收口\",\"likes\":55,\"retweets\":1,\"replies\":9,\"views\":11666,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T12:38:30.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/real_kai42/status/2043307771693760755\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@cherylnatsu\",\"name\":\"夏雨婷\",\"text\":\"看到一群牛逼哄哄的看上去可能是宣称自己在搞“AI”的人在互相割韭菜不知道是卖课还是在干啥\",\"likes\":11,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":4,\"views\":942,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T03:50:59.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/cherylnatsu/status/2043537408621523367\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@anorth_chen\",\"name\":\"North@CreaoAI\",\"text\":\"在对大量agent用户的使用数据进行分析后，传统的C端或B端用户已经不再能简单描述一个新的用户画像。当AI Native的组织模式出现，我把这批人称之为“架构操盘手”，他们通过杠杆agent完成了生产力指数级别的放大，引领着微型巨头的崛起。\",\"likes\":4,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":1,\"views\":268,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:24:14.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/anorth_chen/status/2043591073398972778\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@Viraelelyon\",\"name\":\"三文魚夢女\",\"text\":\"做成了！\",\"likes\":28,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":5,\"views\":1678,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T13:45:55.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/Viraelelyon/status/2043324740388229626\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@huolongguodomgt\",\"name\":\"龙共火火\",\"text\":\"对于老板来说，比起 ai 编程更需要补上的是产品经理课。身边很多老板 ai 编程的使用路径：不屑一顾觉得没啥用——发现居然能做小游戏或者网站——感觉自己可以改变世界——感觉又能干好多业务了——公司又要牛逼——疯狂叫员工去用——好吧员工都是傻逼——连续 干 2 个月，发现没找到落地点。\",\"likes\":11,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":2,\"views\":1493,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T20:46:41.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/huolongguodomgt/status/2043430628348293531\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@shao__meng\",\"name\":\"meng shao\",\"text\":\"我来填坑了：\\nSVG 手绘动画 Skills 基础动画类型生成我先开源出来：\\n\\nhttps://\\ngithub.com/shaom/svg-hand\\n-drawn-skill\\n…\\n\\n输入 SVG 文件后使用「SVG Hand-Drawn Preview Skill」可以直接输出两个文件：\\n1. SVG 手绘动画预览 HTML 页面\\n2. 可以集成到你自己页面的 JS 文件\\n\\n开源项目里也放了下面视频中的预览页面和 SVG 文件。\",\"likes\":87,\"retweets\":21,\"replies\":5,\"views\":8068,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T01:05:47.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/shao__meng/status/2043495831777751324\",\"external_links\":[\"https://github.com/shaom/svg-hand-drawn-skill…\"],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":true},{\"handle\":\"@elonmusk\",\"name\":\"Elon Musk\",\"text\":\"True, use 𝕏 Chat/DMs instead!\",\"likes\":18723,\"retweets\":2391,\"replies\":1955,\"views\":9606922,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T17:20:04.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/2043378630261461446\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@tandfonline\",\"name\":\"Taylor & Francis Research Insights\",\"text\":\"Journals and academic ebooks seeing strong usage and citation growth are shaping Science and Technology research. Is your collection keeping pace?\",\"likes\":0,\"retweets\":0,\"replies\":0,\"views\":0,\"timestamp\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/tandfonline/status/2039162564685508999/analytics\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":true,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@luoleiorg\",\"name\":\"luolei\",\"text\":\"阿里云 Coding Plan Lite 今天18点彻底停售，连老用户续费通道都关了。不少朋友在纠结要不要升 Pro，我的建议是升，找 2–3 人拼车就行，每人每天 1000+ 次请求，正常用根本打不满。\\n\\n我自己选国产 Coding Plan 的逻辑很简单\\n这种不按 Token\",\"likes\":31,\"retweets\":4,\"replies\":15,\"views\":12734,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-13T07:10:44.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/luoleiorg/status/2043587676486651969\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false},{\"handle\":\"@liyue_ai\",\"name\":\"李岳\",\"text\":\"Codex的额度消耗的太快了，\\n正好小米这几天免费使用，\\n我的Hermes Agent已经用上了，\\n下午一直在Vibe Coding，\\n量大管饱，真不错。\\n@Xiaomi\\n\\n注意，要通过Nous Portal这里进入\\n否则需要花钱钱的。\",\"likes\":40,\"retweets\":5,\"replies\":13,\"views\":21648,\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-12T10:08:25.000Z\",\"url\":\"https://x.com/liyue_ai/status/2043270003223622137\",\"external_links\":[],\"is_promoted\":false,\"has_product_signal\":false}]"